February 2020 Master Plumber Board Exam Result

The Professional Regulation Commission (PRC) and the Board of Master Plumbers announces the passers of February 2020 Master Plumber Board Exam Result. Held in NCR, Baguio and Ilo-ilo last February 9-10, 2020. The result is expected in two (2) working days from the last day of examination.

The Board Exam Coverage

February 9, 2020

1. Plumbing Arithmetic

2. Sanitation, Plumbing Design and Installation

February 10, 2020

1. Plumbing Code

2. Practical Problems

February 2020 Real Estate Consultants Board Exam Result

The Professional Regulation Commission (PRC) and the Board of Real Estate Service announces the passers of February 2020 Real Estate Consultants Board Exam Result. Held in Manila last December 8, 2019 for Written Exam and January 17, 18, 19, 29 and 21, 2020 for Revalida. The result is expected in three (3) working days from the last day of examination.

The detailed Board Exam Coverage

December 8, 2019

1. Fundamentals of Real Estate Consulting

2. Professional Consultancy Practice

Revalida

1. Project Feasibility Study

2. Defense/Revalida of the PFS

February 2020 Mechanical Engineer Board Exam Result

The Professional Regulation Commission (PRC) and the Board of Mechanical Engineering announces the 1,334 out of 3,469 passers of February 2020 Mechanical Engineer Board Exam Result. Held in Manila, Baguio, Cebu and Lucena last February 23-24, 2020. The result was released on February 27, 2020, in 2 working days.

The detailed Board Exam Coverage

February 23, 2020

1. Industrial & Power Plant Engineering

February 24, 2020

1. Mathematics,Engineering Economics and Basic Engineering Services

2. Machine Design, Materials and Shop Practice.
